<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-EC9DCDAE-FC80-4BF9-8B65-2612AF54E279" version="2" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-EC9DCDAE-FC80-4BF9-8B65-2612AF54E279" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">How to unpack the printer</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="M028334-B18"><p class="- topic/p ">This document shows you how to unpack the printer and to remove the printer from the pallet. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Video: 
<xref class="- topic/xref " format="html" href="http://localhost:20346/VIDEO00394EN.US/video08/index.html" scope="external"><?ditaot usertext?>How to unpack the printer</xref> 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Installation</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><prereq id="GUID-C71E4B56-F6A6-429E-9630-3F0443D53874" class="- topic/section task/prereq "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li id="LI_C37F34C88B384321AFF4C40DDD852E07" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Check that the location is large enough. You have to have enough room to guide the printer of the pallet. 
</p></li><li id="LI_D233D2ECD6F84F16A6A9BC3C98112ED0" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Makes sure the floor is flat. Bumps or tilts may damage the printer in the process. 
</p></li><li id="LI_3C93FFFF0C3B40A9846FDE4EB11C6906" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> 2 People are required to carry out this procedure. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Make sure you keep the sticker (on the crate or foil on the top cover) that contains the mac address, serial number and software version. You need this info during the installation process. 
</p></li></ol></prereq><section id="SECTION_BB8C533001C043A9B5E24F6EEECB8B53" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Personal protection</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-C8810ABE-05AA-47B2-A506-D909EB952778" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Wear safety shoes when working with heavy material (e.g. installation) or dis-assemblies of units. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Wear protected clothing for protection of your personal clothing. 
</p></note></section><section id="SECTION_0C3117AA47E845948FE99C8DF21ECCCC" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-2A0793C6-47D2-4C38-B4F3-82F35F6E590B" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-AEE1543E-CFB6-40F6-8A13-CAF70AA34194-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-AEE1543E-CFB6-40F6-8A13-CAF70AA34194-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_3EAAE870561847F1914DAA1BC10E2FD6" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_3397BAAC9D5940BDBB97249F1BE4C31D" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_82240E45AAA5452084E7E08BD56CD707" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open ended spanner 17 and 19 or Allen key wrench 6 mm 
</p></li><li id="LI_CB1E4686BB85462D8888B625E861F0C3" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Large screwdriver 
</p></li><li id="LI_D862DB96F2CE4E5386AF2EE0148387F5" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T25 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Electric screwdriver 
</p></li><li id="LI_4FF247D919564A309F1C0709ED147240" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Knife or a side cutter 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Hammer. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> socket wrench SW17 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-8F18057B-2403-4184-99C4-560EB043D7F8" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "/></section><section id="GUID-94C20406-75A1-4BD0-A7DB-8CD9777F04B0" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to unpack</title><table id="NEW" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p translate="yes" class="- topic/p ">Check the label:<ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph "> Exit side</ph> on the crate. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Position the crate, in such a way, that you can roll off the printer easily. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-6967D2F5-F48C-433E-8176-5EA72CE8AD4B" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D4CD08F0-C6D1-4440-A49A-3822C9AD7A38-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D4CD08F0-C6D1-4440-A49A-3822C9AD7A38-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the top cover: 
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the screws (T25) using an electric screwdriver. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the topcover 
</p><note id="GUID-CFF92969-E6C1-450F-8425-0929C12F977C" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Two persons needed to reduce the risk of injury. 
</p></note></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-FFF1415D-84BF-450B-8C52-76C91D5973A1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-CC425CA1-C34F-4667-BDD7-6674F3C8F554-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-CC425CA1-C34F-4667-BDD7-6674F3C8F554-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-8AD6899D-EC73-48B5-B606-F76C54AC1AEE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-27DC3870-A443-4465-B9DD-02BDDE2440F9-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-27DC3870-A443-4465-B9DD-02BDDE2440F9-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove all side covers one by one. 
</p><ol id="OL_6738F3680BE0478FB626CC2AB9112351" class="- topic/ol "><li id="LI_2F4C1CB3A40B46F7A919E83436BFD9A7" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">First</b>: Remove screws (T25) using an electric Screwdriver. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the side covers (4x). 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-62619220-3281-4751-B729-A67FD2AFC5E1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D220AC0B-F6D0-4677-B6B9-B17053762E2F-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D220AC0B-F6D0-4677-B6B9-B17053762E2F-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-1D3C8E18-B8ED-479B-8A82-11FCB62ABC9F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-C63A9BA3-4D52-42B7-AED7-58E4E8A9D0B3-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C63A9BA3-4D52-42B7-AED7-58E4E8A9D0B3-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-B4F0CB68-B3D5-469D-8DAD-6D40A906307A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-60E41BD9-4C8B-4A6A-8095-F8E89171DD68-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-60E41BD9-4C8B-4A6A-8095-F8E89171DD68-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-9B04F939-5975-4356-9B9F-951369A6166C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCEC213C-DEDF-4AB2-9AFE-7E58FA05DE11-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCEC213C-DEDF-4AB2-9AFE-7E58FA05DE11-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the User documentation and Printer driver notice. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-6D7CDD99-445F-4F04-A0E3-785F7DE76540" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-48998F4B-2A71-4673-A5EE-2710DB98E129-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-48998F4B-2A71-4673-A5EE-2710DB98E129-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-72C7568D-CFE2-40AF-BACF-248C930945D1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-758BC63D-961A-4570-B008-06DFA23FF8F2-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-758BC63D-961A-4570-B008-06DFA23FF8F2-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Cut the aluminum bag at the bottom. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-0245FF06-C7C1-445D-A585-6180A1987510" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-120A2D99-C51B-46A3-9DE5-589AF250C131-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-120A2D99-C51B-46A3-9DE5-589AF250C131-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the aluminum bag to the top. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-7CE10AF5-A9C2-4BB3-8592-0D12FA227425" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-70BE9E83-6613-4BDB-8BB7-DD5F7015AFF7-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-70BE9E83-6613-4BDB-8BB7-DD5F7015AFF7-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the foil wrapped around the printer. 
</p><note id="GUID-ACB6E771-89A2-4635-AC13-EE66BB00CA28" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Do not remove the foil from the top cover. Leave it as protection during the installation. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-0F13D833-F2B5-453E-B30A-DBB3F025A6AE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-42CF602B-9010-4930-B956-C1BBFE658E1A-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-42CF602B-9010-4930-B956-C1BBFE658E1A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Sticker with serial number, MAC address and software version on the foil of the top cover. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-30AA1753-B90A-4576-B6E4-F76A6A533D05" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-35DAD23E-BA0E-4E43-B53E-6347A97C3098-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-35DAD23E-BA0E-4E43-B53E-6347A97C3098-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the foams and tapes around the printer: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Top cover 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Winder 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Winder left hand side 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Winder right hand side 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Wheels 
</p></li></ul></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-D7B52A24-0C24-47DA-8FAF-032537F03A4A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-A1A5005E-AA54-494A-9B02-6DF36D79A0E7-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-A1A5005E-AA54-494A-9B02-6DF36D79A0E7-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-2ECFA1A0-0AE5-4A94-A060-891A407690C4" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F8D0BBFB-6705-488A-8D1A-0891526C349D-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F8D0BBFB-6705-488A-8D1A-0891526C349D-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-3F5B1BE9-415E-4788-8C83-8FD32A8B5705" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-05BE9DB3-7838-42E3-861C-3C17D6A866C2-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-05BE9DB3-7838-42E3-861C-3C17D6A866C2-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-743C1CBE-B53E-41F6-90C6-2A89F0DE410F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-DD3493DA-A0F9-4CB1-B61B-40D9A103551D-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DD3493DA-A0F9-4CB1-B61B-40D9A103551D-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-A9CCC065-CD86-4597-86F7-FB4BFD33DE69" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-94DD7ECD-5C48-4AEB-9254-87C32178F670-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-94DD7ECD-5C48-4AEB-9254-87C32178F670-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-5BB8639A-1CAD-48B5-AFE0-82DAEE69B7B0" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-2F55FCBA-7B88-4DE0-AD25-DD42DF0112F5-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-2F55FCBA-7B88-4DE0-AD25-DD42DF0112F5-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-4012E58A-3B54-46D7-BCA7-4DD3472C39E3" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-7CC8CBEF-B328-4656-BBF0-2B781782E537-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-7CC8CBEF-B328-4656-BBF0-2B781782E537-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 10 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 4 bags with silica gel. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-DB9183E9-19CB-4AC7-B14A-2AA35F634538" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-516F0996-15F1-43EA-A847-5F4EE3A13E56-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-516F0996-15F1-43EA-A847-5F4EE3A13E56-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-A49A8F6C-3687-4C8A-A8B6-A165A3803C0C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B9FA5B2D-EC2F-4930-90F9-631B915CB9DA-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B9FA5B2D-EC2F-4930-90F9-631B915CB9DA-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">11 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">At the winder side: 
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Lift the guide plate of the winder. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 2 foam blocks below the guide plate. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-1124240A-2F6B-4456-A76E-299581418032" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-3F536443-A0EB-41E1-AA3A-2F8B955F2893-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-3F536443-A0EB-41E1-AA3A-2F8B955F2893-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-181045C6-9D49-476E-8DEC-36EE41797959" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0D61CB2C-36CB-4526-AA8D-A1DC0A751613-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0D61CB2C-36CB-4526-AA8D-A1DC0A751613-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-C27C61B8-BE74-4F07-9197-973C140911F8" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-60B9FCE5-5EDB-41C0-A3C0-3A260EED6753-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-60B9FCE5-5EDB-41C0-A3C0-3A260EED6753-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">12 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Cut the 2 cable ties. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the packages carefully below the printer. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Transport these 2 packages to the final installation location. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-E67E6F4E-C0AA-4D9B-B1EC-03D1AE66A1FA" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-7095A74B-C6F5-46FB-8E76-39CC9F87253B-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-7095A74B-C6F5-46FB-8E76-39CC9F87253B-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-461EA188-D35C-4C2E-9C14-6EDE466BAAAD" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4C01C6AA-D04D-4F3D-AE48-FB9B2CC7701F-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4C01C6AA-D04D-4F3D-AE48-FB9B2CC7701F-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-B71BE596-E1AB-4797-9151-B416D2A0815E" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F8D8C9A7-F5A8-4046-B167-5A7342D0CDAB-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F8D8C9A7-F5A8-4046-B167-5A7342D0CDAB-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">13 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the cover plate. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-F64E8351-6399-42E1-BF63-E4FD772F48F4" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-7D2E78E0-B116-47FF-9D3D-FC6E4F34C923-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-7D2E78E0-B116-47FF-9D3D-FC6E4F34C923-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">14 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Cut the horizontal transportation strap. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-86EC2530-943E-48AA-BA62-F7843B16DE67" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-95BE5FCA-A0E9-4C90-940F-CF83660C7291-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-95BE5FCA-A0E9-4C90-940F-CF83660C7291-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">15 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 3 screws located under the pallet to release the chiller from the pallet. (sw17) 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-B4196132-A4FA-4DB6-81B5-F94B5BAA76BD" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-53996562-F052-4CE7-97B1-831CB7DCB37F-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-53996562-F052-4CE7-97B1-831CB7DCB37F-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">16 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Move the chiller from the pallet using the handles. 
</p><note id="GUID-1C38A923-129C-4CEF-9D53-4BC3278260FE" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Two persons needed to reduce the risk of injury. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-69D0C7D7-6EDF-4BF6-8496-2C5A9596596E" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0093C8F9-DEAE-4978-AAA0-584A79FB3A31-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0093C8F9-DEAE-4978-AAA0-584A79FB3A31-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-A82DD27E-1A07-4059-8B6A-197969A2C4A8" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-65C6F772-696C-404A-88C2-56A84A326D77-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-65C6F772-696C-404A-88C2-56A84A326D77-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">17 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the bolts of the 2 rubber buffer blocks below the media drawer. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-F3FDE946-507B-40E0-8AD3-F49F8E64C0BF" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-DFCA9981-4F66-47E1-8CD3-F56015EDCE2F-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DFCA9981-4F66-47E1-8CD3-F56015EDCE2F-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">18 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the bolts of the 2 brackets below the winder (17 mm). 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the brackets. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-B8D95139-E850-4F13-8244-B31244913089" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E2BFEE82-4850-4CDC-99E8-83901CE9A583-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E2BFEE82-4850-4CDC-99E8-83901CE9A583-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-B77670F4-1EFA-4C7F-B488-916B311376D6" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-76E82749-60DD-416F-B497-8DFDFAAE0C01-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-76E82749-60DD-416F-B497-8DFDFAAE0C01-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">19 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the bolts of the 2 brackets below the media drawer. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the brackets 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-D24C6BDC-35B0-48F7-BA48-C11D9C18BEBC" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-2D61F815-3263-4DF7-93BD-73F4FB704B2A-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-2D61F815-3263-4DF7-93BD-73F4FB704B2A-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-1EC7A33F-4047-488F-B9B1-8862645F0D06" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6A67C329-DD4B-4386-B507-67F6625D59C6-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6A67C329-DD4B-4386-B507-67F6625D59C6-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">20 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Lower the 4 leveling adjustment screws on all 4 corners (Open ended spanner 19 mm or Allen key wrench 6 mm). 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">If needed: adapt the position of the wooden block with a hammer. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Lift the printer until there is a few mm gap between the engine and the U shaped bracket. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Do this with all 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">4</b> leveling bolts (Open ended spanner 19 mm or Allen key wrench 6 mm). 
</p><note type="caution" id="GUID-743C4B17-E24C-42EF-8E95-76C514E10FC4" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">The printer is now positioned on the 4 leveling bolts on the pallet. 
</p></note></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-00DBE5A4-7323-461F-BDE2-BE2A5DA15410" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-15BD5502-903D-4474-A748-44F766C7A714-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-15BD5502-903D-4474-A748-44F766C7A714-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-7430DF77-A140-45E4-A6A3-2B09C5C79075" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B267AD4A-D9F7-4235-A913-9A2B57098FD6-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B267AD4A-D9F7-4235-A913-9A2B57098FD6-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-201FBADD-60DE-4CB4-B063-B3B8E8D0A1A6" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-79A27994-02C3-4121-B85F-DD9B976DA9F9-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-79A27994-02C3-4121-B85F-DD9B976DA9F9-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">21 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 2 U-shape profiles. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-2DE5426B-2B9B-44AC-BF7F-2D7277CB5EC1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-792895F2-5CB3-4B82-B0DE-CD9ADED40368-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-792895F2-5CB3-4B82-B0DE-CD9ADED40368-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-D4859F3D-8B96-4939-BD3F-9F88F9861D8F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-40656B95-097C-4F55-A407-8EDB308C3CD5-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-40656B95-097C-4F55-A407-8EDB308C3CD5-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-0EE86F01-4238-404B-A089-6A8A65BD38FF" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-EAEA254B-2D3A-413F-A47E-E39A9A2E7835-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-EAEA254B-2D3A-413F-A47E-E39A9A2E7835-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">22 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove wooden block (exit side) 3 screws (T25) 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-47884AAD-032C-4E38-A9B8-E38D78B60536" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-EEBD171D-39AB-44F7-ACFD-9BA0D4046B08-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-EEBD171D-39AB-44F7-ACFD-9BA0D4046B08-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">23 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Cut some extra aluminum foil out of the way to make sure the ramp can be mounted properly and the printer moves easily. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-D7E664DF-6047-48CA-8B31-62B6915AE020" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1FA14560-334D-4A41-B263-DA2E45FDC118-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1FA14560-334D-4A41-B263-DA2E45FDC118-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">24 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Turn the 4 wheels in the correct direction (The roll off position is in the pictures at the left hand side). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-B5E5DF07-AE9B-42B3-A9C3-A8122339DF7E" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E24DF063-7F23-492B-BF56-78BC79D7979F-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E24DF063-7F23-492B-BF56-78BC79D7979F-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">25 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Lower the printer onto the 4 wheels with the 4 leveling bolts. (step by step) 
</p><note id="GUID-3E6FE360-6D2B-46CF-93C6-2C318B94B307" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Do not do it all at once. Go half the way at all 4 corners before you continue. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-AFA87515-C435-4823-9ECA-F59F0FA93229" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-46398CC1-7BAF-4888-8C8F-7B2EA4EAA9B1-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-46398CC1-7BAF-4888-8C8F-7B2EA4EAA9B1-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">26 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Unscrew the 4 rubber blocks. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-C14C03D9-F8B1-4BDE-A3EF-90462E424E71" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-A3B9BA08-AAF5-44DE-BBD8-179C0451EAB0-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-A3B9BA08-AAF5-44DE-BBD8-179C0451EAB0-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">27 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 4 wooden blocks. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-DCB06F45-E692-425D-97F8-038E89159D68" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-8FE2D5E5-3E50-4796-A031-332F5ED6EA2D-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-8FE2D5E5-3E50-4796-A031-332F5ED6EA2D-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">28 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 2 U-shaped bars and 4 bolts from the pallet. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-D7690366-5EB4-4E7A-A924-6C1D00432B26" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4B047BC0-A3DE-4E0B-9E13-957EF2F1ECE3-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4B047BC0-A3DE-4E0B-9E13-957EF2F1ECE3-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">29 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Cut the aluminum foil to free the 4 weels. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Place the 2 U-shaped bars on the pallet to create the ramp. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> The ramp will allow you to ride the printer of the pallet. 
</p></li></ol><note id="GUID-11AD55D6-D7D4-4FB7-A78F-ADC752D6A727" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Watch the correct position of the 2 bars: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Right hand side: Longest edge at the right hand side. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Left hand side: Longest edge at the left hand side. 
</p></li></ul></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-1F138020-9DFA-4549-B75D-D9235E651EEF" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E8323FBA-B330-44D9-A655-87739B2F265A-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E8323FBA-B330-44D9-A655-87739B2F265A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">30 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 people should now push/pull the printer towards the ramp. 
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-FB6F27DA-906E-4E18-8179-D3C65CE72913" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Push the printer only at the metal part as shown in the picture. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Never push at the transparent part of the top cover. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-9A49EF07-E618-47EF-851F-5730C080EA7B" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-205DF840-9A98-42CD-A307-11689E67715E-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-205DF840-9A98-42CD-A307-11689E67715E-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-11B14C23-09F3-418E-972C-6F9469569A16" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-4D116DA7-8E88-4A35-BDB5-11AE16DD6DDF-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-4D116DA7-8E88-4A35-BDB5-11AE16DD6DDF-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">31 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Align the printer properly with the rail and then move the printer downwards until the first pair of wheels are on the floor. 
</p><note id="GUID-A5AF7453-F7FB-420C-943F-03A4D5B3A6C0" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">If the floor is not flat or too soft the printer can touch the pallet in this step. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-34EB5745-B42F-4CA5-9425-8FBDA0C2C19A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-DE1FEF17-55EF-48D9-B43E-F389A89AA586-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DE1FEF17-55EF-48D9-B43E-F389A89AA586-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">32 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Place the printer on the floor. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-67C34F1B-BD23-4ADB-9F19-44D8972C26EB" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-79079226-3969-440E-A294-119D36874687-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-79079226-3969-440E-A294-119D36874687-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">33 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Transport the printer to the final location. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Leave the top cover protection sheet on the top cover until the installation is finished. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-04FB760D-2A76-4AA0-A124-AA4EA8B4A405" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-59CFB746-93C4-47C0-B031-AABE9FD35EB8-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-59CFB746-93C4-47C0-B031-AABE9FD35EB8-low.png"/><image href="GUID-02C49451-2381-4848-84F0-48F42C8DB24D-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-02C49451-2381-4848-84F0-48F42C8DB24D-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">34 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove and or dispose the pallet and transport materials. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-3955AF8F-9BF3-4DD3-AA2A-175FB2AE2E43.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Installation</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
</task>